        "**Breaking dependencies incorrectly**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Code splitting is a powerful optimization technique that reduces load time and improves performance. It ensures users load only what they need, making applications faster and more efficient."
    }
